body_html: Expanding it out to the union of modules in the filetree and the current list seems fine. I assume there are some modules in the filetree that aren't explicitly imported by one of their parents or tested by the tests in tf_tests.cmake, and so we've been getting away with having fewer modules in the CMake files.

body: Expanding it out to the union of modules in the filetree and the current list seems fine.
